{"tid":495614,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買中移動收5厘息","createTime":"2017-12-10T23:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T11:07:28.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"39ef315375101745be51566ab73e04c9d8b636d4","tid":495614,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T23:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171208/large/18238127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171208%2Flarge%2F18238127.jpg&h=172481a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中移動派息能力高強。圖為董事長尚冰。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中移動（941）昨日最低76.25元，創近兩年新低，收報76.6元。中移動由年初起計，跌3%，跑輸聯通（762）的18%升幅及中電信（728）的5%。恒指今年最高升37%，現時升幅29%。對於有「畏高症」的股民，中移動是追落後及收息對象，當然不能急功近利。<br />\n<br />\n1）大行平均給予中移動目標價101.01元（潛在升幅33%），最高3家平均114.53元（潛在升幅50%）。不宜照單全收，宜打打折。<br />\n<br />\n2）今年上半年，中移動營業額3,889億元人幣，按年增5%，純利627億元人幣，微升3.5%。彭博綜合券商預測，今年全年賺1,140億元人幣，增長5%。由2007年至2017年，中移動盈利增長僅31%。盈利高增長期已過，過去9年股價呆呆滯滯，2007年10月恒指見3萬2時例外，當時中移動高見154元（PE39倍，PB6.7倍；如此估值，當然難以長守）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目標價95元</strong><br />\n<br />\n3）中移動往績PE12.1倍，今年預期11.6倍，較10年平均13.4倍折讓1成3；在盈利較高增長的前10年（1997至2007年），平均PE為30倍。聯通今年預期PE50倍，中電信12.7倍，中移動較同業平均低得多。<br />\n<br />\n4）中移動今年預期PB1.33倍，較10年平均2.2倍折讓4成，高過聯通與中電信平均的0.84倍。<br />\n<br />\n5）中移動今年中期已派例息1.62元及特息3.2元，共4.82元，估計末期派1.8元，全年6.62元，折合股息率高達8.6厘。聯通今年預期股息率僅0.9厘，中電信3.2厘。明年，中移動特息料不續派或大減，每股派息3.8元，股息率將降至5厘，收息仍屬理想。<br />\n<br />\n今年6月底，中移動手上現金及可供出售金融資產高達4,840億元人幣（借貸僅50億元），每股28港元，派息能力高強。<br />\n<br />\n★在恒指成份股中，中移動是今年的「第3狗」（中石油（857）及聯想（992）跌幅大過中移動），在紅指成份股中是「第2狗」（聯想是第1狗），適合畏高症股民作為收息對象。<br />\n<br />\n明年股息率5厘，以降至4厘為目標，目標價95元，上升空間24%。明年5G概念若受落，目標價可以高一點。<br />\n<br />\n何車<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171208/20238597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F20238597&d=smd8PAPZq11A2qEuW46VUP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=71c05f25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171208%2F20238597&h=389e42fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171208/20238597</a>"},{"pid":"28fa9304972ad2a99e45dc25cc31da569dca0151","tid":495614,"uid":27591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T23:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2577d1286992ea497adfd77f8ed55857426ba619","tid":495614,"uid":23536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:14:27.000Z","msg":"大行前排不斷唱衰佢5G業務投資過大 叫人減接 宜家講股佬叫人買 兩邊唱雙簧呀？"},{"pid":"1247f0d06d680e0f5a91ba1de25563baaf7cd8a4","tid":495614,"uid":23536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:15:05.000Z","msg":"大行前排不斷唱衰佢5G業務投資過大 叫人減持 宜家講股佬叫人買 兩邊唱雙簧呀？"},{"pid":"a337e6749ea2c912d75fe2a180cc48ee52daf4da","tid":495614,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"報紙叫人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617c970129512c5685ad6fe37c56416480aed5d4","tid":495614,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"95<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8470629e9dd3044c33443bf08ef59e6a482824","tid":495614,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:51:24.000Z","msg":"當年股王被國策搞死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4629bf62cd40eb848da090d6fc175a9d61ea7086","tid":495614,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:40:43.000Z","msg":"60蚊就入"},{"pid":"6e524c9a2d491c238c991174d8e75951d517c708","tid":495614,"uid":30604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"千股 屌你老味"},{"pid":"c0982bbb700fe1b305b942f90519d45146987e97","tid":495614,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好撚入 </span>"},{"pid":"5cdf90942bd421bc8df4d0f37f7bea2d754e4d00","tid":495614,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"2015 年好時吹到破120 蚊<br />\n<br />\n呃曬傻散入貨時, SIR 到落8X<br />\n<br />\n而家2017 年成個升浪都無郁過, 仲下試 70"},{"pid":"966236f60bca5fc2eaccce41f23d1e276d8787b7","tid":495614,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:56:42.000Z","msg":"但要扣股息稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e9c705f3c24b5d1c3f9295394ef21cc875b659","tid":495614,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"咁不如PCCW"},{"pid":"8b2666a128a8ecbc0b4c735cfef525d63f1cdc94","tid":495614,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"何車仲未收檔？"},{"pid":"53c6f15e1745d801acaacb3657cc9e67513af9e2","tid":495614,"uid":146611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"中移動 已經變成公用股"},{"pid":"5f96b3548878ed5c7b7fcf39bd1865b3818c2f8b","tid":495614,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}